        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Chop your <strong>coriander</strong> finely, including the stalks (save a few whole leaves for garnish!)</p><p>Combine your <strong>mayo</strong> with your <strong>white wine vinegar</strong>, <strong>chopped</strong> <strong>coriander</strong> and a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> – this is your <strong>coriander mayo</strong></p><p>Wash your<strong> lettuce</strong> and pat it dry with kitchen paper, then shred it roughly</p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-1647347820708-x200.jpg",
