            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>To assemble your Baja-style tacos, divide the <strong>shredded lettuce </strong>and <strong>roasted onion & peppers</strong> between the <strong>warmed tortillas</strong></p><p>Top each tortilla with<strong> </strong>2 <strong>crispy tofu strips</strong> and a drizzle of the <strong>coriander mayo</strong></p><p>Garnish with the <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>coriander leaves</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
      "order": 8,
